---
const repoUrl = 'https://github.com/tame-gg/SilkMC';
const releaseUrl = 'https://github.com/tame-gg/SilkMC/releases/latest';
const paperclipUrl = 'https://github.com/tame-gg/SilkMC/releases/download/v0.1.1-alpha/silkmc-paperclip-26.1.2.local-SNAPSHOT.jar';
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>SilkMC - Multithreaded Minecraft Server Platform</title>
  <meta name="description" content="SilkMC is a Folia-derived Minecraft server platform focused on regional multithreading, practical plugin compatibility, and safer alpha testing." />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://koels.site/silkmc" />
  <meta property="og:title" content="SilkMC - Multithreaded Minecraft Server Platform" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="Regional multithreading with pragmatic Paper, Bukkit, and Spigot plugin compatibility work." />
  <meta property="og:site_name" content="SilkMC" />
  <meta property="og:image" content="https://koels.site/silkmc-hero.png" />
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
  <meta name="twitter:image" content="https://koels.site/silkmc-hero.png" />
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://koels.site/silkmc" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    @view-transition { navigation: auto; }

    :root {
      --ink: #e8f8ff;
      --paper: #020810;
      --paper-2: #040e1e;
      --paper-3: #06162b;
      --muted: rgba(200, 240, 255, 0.62);
      --quiet: rgba(200, 240, 255, 0.34);
      --line: rgba(64, 200, 255, 0.14);
      --line-strong: rgba(64, 200, 255, 0.28);
      --moss: #00ffcc;
      --pine: #041827;
      --copper: #40c8ff;
      --aqua: #40c8ff;
      --danger: #ff6b7a;
      --shadow: 0 34px 110px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.58);
      --sans: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
      --mono: 'JetBrains Mono', ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, monospace;
    }

    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; background: var(--paper); }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: var(--sans);
      color: var(--ink);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 18% 0%, rgba(0, 96, 176, 0.28), transparent 34rem),
        radial-gradient(circle at 76% 18%, rgba(0, 255, 204, 0.12), transparent 32rem),
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(2, 8, 16, 0.72), rgba(2, 8, 16, 1) 720px),
        var(--paper);
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }
    body::before {
      content: '';
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      z-index: -1;
      pointer-events: none;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(64, 200, 255, 0.055) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(64, 200, 255, 0.055) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 32px 32px;
      mask-image: linear-gradient(180deg, black, transparent 82%);
    }
    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    code { font-family: var(--mono); }

    .site-nav {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      z-index: 20;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 24px;
      height: 64px;
      padding: 0 clamp(18px, 4vw, 56px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(2, 8, 16, 0.78);
      backdrop-filter: blur(24px);
    }

    .brand {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .brand-mark {
      width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      background: rgba(64, 200, 255, 0.08);
      color: var(--moss);
      border: 1px solid var(--line-strong);
      box-shadow: 0 0 22px rgba(0, 255, 204, 0.18);
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 22px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--ink); }

    .nav-button {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      min-height: 36px;
      padding: 0 13px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line-strong);
      background: rgba(64, 200, 255, 0.06);
      color: var(--ink);
    }

    .nav-button:hover { border-color: var(--moss); }

    .hero {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 88vh;
      display: grid;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 96px clamp(18px, 5vw, 72px) 54px;
      isolation: isolate;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      z-index: -2;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(2, 8, 16, 0.98) 0%, rgba(2, 8, 16, 0.75) 42%, rgba(2, 8, 16, 0.26) 74%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(2, 8, 16, 0.08), rgba(2, 8, 16, 0.96) 94%),
        url('/silkmc-hero.png');
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
    }

    .hero::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      z-index: -1;
      opacity: 0.42;
      background-image:
        radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 48px 48px;
      mask-image: linear-gradient(90deg, black, transparent 74%);
    }

    .hero-shell {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.96fr) minmax(330px, 0.58fr);
      gap: clamp(24px, 5vw, 74px);
      align-items: center;
      width: min(1180px, 100%);
    }

    .hero-content {
      width: min(720px, 100%);
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
      color: var(--moss);
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .eyebrow::before {
      content: '';
      width: 28px;
      height: 2px;
      background: var(--moss);
    }

    h1, h2, h3, p { margin: 0; }

    h1 {
      max-width: 760px;
      color: #f0fbff;
      font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 6.2vw, 5.35rem);
      line-height: 0.96;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .hero-copy {
      max-width: 620px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.5vw, 1.22rem);
      line-height: 1.68;
    }

    .actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }

    .hero-alert {
      margin-top: 16px;
      display: inline-flex;
      max-width: 620px;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 107, 122, 0.34);
      background: rgba(255, 107, 122, 0.075);
      color: #ffc6ce;
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      line-height: 1.55;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      min-height: 46px;
      padding: 0 18px;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      transition: transform 160ms ease, border-color 160ms ease, background 160ms ease;
    }

    .button svg { width: 15px; height: 15px; }
    .button:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); }
    .button.primary {
      background: var(--aqua);
      color: #010810;
      box-shadow: 0 0 28px rgba(64, 200, 255, 0.24);
    }
    .button.secondary { border-color: var(--line-strong); background: rgba(2, 12, 28, 0.7); color: var(--ink); }
    .button.secondary:hover { border-color: var(--copper); }

    .alpha-panel,
    .terminal-panel {
      border: 1px solid var(--line-strong);
      background: rgba(2, 12, 28, 0.72);
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.035);
    }

    .terminal-panel {
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .terminal-bar {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(64, 200, 255, 0.11);
      color: var(--quiet);
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.66rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .terminal-dots {
      display: flex;
      gap: 6px;
    }

    .terminal-dots span {
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(64, 200, 255, 0.24);
    }

    .terminal-body {
      padding: 18px;
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      line-height: 1.86;
    }

    .line-dim { color: rgba(200, 240, 255, 0.34); }
    .line-key { color: var(--ink); }
    .line-val { color: var(--moss); }
    .line-warn {
      display: block;
      margin: 8px -18px 0;
      padding: 8px 18px;
      border-left: 2px solid var(--danger);
      background: rgba(255, 107, 122, 0.08);
      color: #ffc6ce;
    }

    .alpha-panel {
      margin-top: 12px;
      padding: 18px;
    }

    .alpha-panel strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      color: var(--danger);
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .alpha-panel p {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .release-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(2, 12, 28, 0.82);
    }

    .release-item {
      min-height: 108px;
      padding: 22px clamp(18px, 3vw, 36px);
      border-right: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .release-item:last-child { border-right: 0; }
    .label {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: var(--quiet);
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.66rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .value {
      color: var(--ink);
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.7vw, 1.28rem);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .band {
      padding: clamp(64px, 9vw, 116px) clamp(18px, 5vw, 72px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .band.alt { background: rgba(4, 14, 30, 0.68); }

    .section-head {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.82fr) minmax(280px, 0.48fr);
      gap: clamp(28px, 6vw, 90px);
      align-items: end;
      margin-bottom: 34px;
    }

    h2 {
      color: #f0fbff;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 4.2rem);
      line-height: 1.02;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .section-copy {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.98rem;
      line-height: 1.75;
    }

    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 12px;
      background: transparent;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      padding: 12px;
      background-color: rgba(2, 12, 28, 0.28);
    }

    .tile {
      min-height: 230px;
      padding: 26px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(64, 200, 255, 0.1);
      background: rgba(2, 12, 28, 0.58);
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
    }

    .tile.alt-bg { background: rgba(4, 22, 43, 0.72); }

    .tile-kicker {
      color: var(--copper);
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.66rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .tile h3 {
      margin-top: 38px;
      color: var(--ink);
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      line-height: 1.25;
    }

    .tile p {
      margin-top: 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      line-height: 1.66;
    }

    .runbook {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.9fr) minmax(300px, 0.58fr);
      gap: 1px;
      background: var(--line);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .command-panel,
    .jar-panel {
      background: rgba(2, 5, 12, 0.88);
      padding: clamp(22px, 4vw, 36px);
    }

    .command-panel pre {
      margin: 0;
      overflow-x: auto;
      color: var(--moss);
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: clamp(0.78rem, 1.15vw, 0.95rem);
      line-height: 1.85;
    }

    .jar-panel {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 32px;
    }

    .jar-panel p {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.72;
    }

    .jar-name {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 12px;
      color: var(--aqua);
      word-break: break-word;
    }

    .warning {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 16px minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 14px;
      align-items: start;
      padding: 18px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(227, 108, 95, 0.32);
      background: rgba(227, 108, 95, 0.08);
      color: #f3c8c2;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      line-height: 1.62;
    }

    .warning-dot {
      width: 12px;
      height: 12px;
      margin-top: 6px;
      background: var(--danger);
    }

    .status-list {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 1px;
      background: var(--line);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .status-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 120px minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
      padding: 22px;
      background: rgba(2, 12, 28, 0.58);
    }

    .status-row strong {
      color: var(--moss);
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .status-row span {
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .footer {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 24px;
      padding: 30px clamp(18px, 5vw, 72px);
      color: var(--quiet);
      font-size: 0.86rem;
    }

    .footer a { color: var(--muted); }
    .footer a:hover { color: var(--ink); }

    @media (max-width: 920px) {
      .nav-links a:not(.nav-button) { display: none; }
      .hero { min-height: 82vh; }
      .release-row { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
      .release-item:nth-child(2) { border-right: 0; }
      .release-item:nth-child(-n + 2) { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
      .section-head,
      .hero-shell,
      .runbook { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .tile { min-height: auto; }
      .tile h3 { margin-top: 24px; }
      .status-list { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 620px) {
      .site-nav { height: 58px; }
      .brand span:last-child { display: none; }
      .nav-button { padding: 0 10px; }
      .hero {
        min-height: 78vh;
        padding-top: 100px;
        padding-bottom: 42px;
      }
      .hero::before {
        background-image:
          linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(18, 20, 20, 0.58) 0%, rgba(18, 20, 20, 0.94) 62%, rgba(18, 20, 20, 1) 100%),
          url('/silkmc-hero.png');
        background-position: 61% center;
      }
      .actions { flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; }
      .release-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .release-item {
        min-height: 92px;
        border-right: 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      }
      .release-item:last-child { border-bottom: 0; }
      .status-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 8px; }
      .footer { flex-direction: column; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="site-nav">
    <a class="brand" href="/" aria-label="Back to koels.site">
      <span class="brand-mark">S</span>
      <span>SilkMC</span>
    </a>
    <nav class="nav-links" aria-label="SilkMC navigation">
      <a href="#status">Status</a>
      <a href="#compatibility">Compatibility</a>
      <a href="#run">Run</a>
      <a class="nav-button" href={repoUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M7 17L17 7M9 7h8v8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
        </svg>
        GitHub
      </a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-shell">
        <div class="hero-content">
          <span class="eyebrow">v0.1.1-alpha public build</span>
          <h1>Region threaded Minecraft servers.</h1>
          <p class="hero-copy">
            SilkMC keeps Folia's regional multithreading model and pushes on the part server owners actually feel first:
            getting more Paper, Bukkit, and Spigot plugin stacks to start, warn clearly, and fail safely when they cross thread boundaries.
          </p>
          <p class="hero-alert">Alpha software: bugs, memory leaks, security issues, data loss, and plugin breakage are possible.</p>
          <div class="actions">
            <a class="button primary" id="download-button" href={paperclipUrl}>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
                <path d="M12 3v12m0 0l-5-5m5 5l5-5M5 21h14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
              </svg>
              Download paperclip jar
            </a>
            <a class="button secondary" href={releaseUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
                <path d="M8 6h13M8 12h13M8 18h13M3 6h.01M3 12h.01M3 18h.01" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
              </svg>
              Release notes
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <aside class="terminal-panel" aria-label="SilkMC alpha status">
            <div class="terminal-bar">
              <div class="terminal-dots" aria-hidden="true"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
              <span>silkmc-status.yml</span>
            </div>
            <div class="terminal-body">
              <span class="line-dim"># current public state</span><br />
              <span class="line-key">release</span>: <span class="line-val">v0.1.1-alpha</span><br />
              <span class="line-key">base</span>: <span class="line-val">Folia 26.1.2</span><br />
              <span class="line-key">runtime</span>: <span class="line-val">JDK 25</span><br />
              <span class="line-warn">alpha: bugs, memory leaks, security issues, and plugin breakage are possible</span>
            </div>
          </aside>
          <aside class="alpha-panel">
            <strong>Alpha warning</strong>
            <p>
              SilkMC is not production-hardened yet. Test it on disposable worlds first; there may be crashes,
              memory leaks, security vulnerabilities, data loss, plugin incompatibilities, or unsafe edge cases.
            </p>
          </aside>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="release-row" id="status" aria-label="SilkMC release status">
      <div class="release-item">
        <span class="label">Latest release</span>
        <span class="value" id="release-name">v0.1.1-alpha</span>
      </div>
      <div class="release-item">
        <span class="label">Upstream base</span>
        <span class="value">Folia 26.1.2</span>
      </div>
      <div class="release-item">
        <span class="label">Runtime</span>
        <span class="value">JDK 25</span>
      </div>
      <div class="release-item">
        <span class="label">License</span>
        <span class="value">GPL-3.0</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="band" id="compatibility">
      <div class="section-head">
        <div>
          <span class="eyebrow">Compatibility stance</span>
          <h2>More useful than pretending every plugin is safe.</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="section-copy">
          SilkMC is compatibility-focused by default, but it does not hide region-thread violations. The project favors
          maintainable shims, visible warnings, and controlled failure paths over changes that trade correctness for a quick startup.
          It is still alpha software, so treat every compatibility win as something to validate under load.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid">
        <article class="tile">
          <span class="tile-kicker">01 / metadata</span>
          <h3>Compatibility-aware plugins get a clear path.</h3>
          <p>Plugins can opt into SilkMC behavior with project metadata while legacy Folia-aware metadata remains honored for upstream interoperability.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="tile alt-bg">
          <span class="tile-kicker">02 / scheduling</span>
          <h3>Common scheduler assumptions are the first target.</h3>
          <p>Legacy sync expectations, lifecycle timing, and task ownership mistakes are the areas where compatibility work can help most without lying about threads.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="tile">
          <span class="tile-kicker">03 / guardrails</span>
          <h3>Unsafe plugin behavior should be readable.</h3>
          <p>When a plugin crosses into behavior SilkMC cannot preserve safely, the goal is a direct warning or disable path instead of a mystery crash.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="band alt" id="run">
      <div class="section-head">
        <div>
          <span class="eyebrow">Run the right artifact</span>
          <h2>The paperclip jar is the server jar.</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="section-copy">
          The latest GitHub release includes multiple jars. For normal startup, use the Paperclip-style jar.
          The plain server module jar is not meant to be launched standalone.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="runbook">
        <div class="command-panel">
          <pre><code>git clone https://github.com/tame-gg/SilkMC.git
cd SilkMC
./gradlew applyAllPatches
./gradlew build
./gradlew :silkmc-server:createPaperclipJar

